ous sizes and types. All values should be either absolute or relative URLs. No effects are added to the \"precomposed\" icons.\";s:4:\"form\";a:1:{s:7:\"#weight\";i:100;}}s:10:\"open-graph\";a:3:{s:5:\"label\";s:10:\"Open Graph\";s:11:\"description\";s:168:\"The <a href=\"http://ogp.me/\">Open Graph meta tags</a> are used control how Facebook, Pinterest, LinkedIn and other social networking sites interpret the site\'s content.\";s:4:\"form\";a:1:{s:7:\"#weight\";i:50;}}}s:4:\"tags\";a:109:{s:5:\"title\";a:6:{s:5:\"label\";s:10:\"Page title\";s:11:\"description\";s:194:\"The text to display in the title bar of a visitor\'s web browser when they view this page. This meta tag may also be used as the title of the page when a visitor bookmarks or favorites this page.\";s:5:\"class\";s:18:\"DrupalTitleMetaTag\";s:5:\"group\";s:5:\"basic\";s:6:\"weight\";i:1;s:4:\"name\";s:5:\"title\";}s:11:\"description\";a:7:{s:5:\"label\";s:11:\"Description\";s:11:\"description\";s:195:\"A brief and concise summary of the page\'s content, preferably 150 characters or less. The description meta tag may be used by search engines to display a snippet about the page in search results.\";s:5:\"class\";s:17:\"DrupalTextMetaTag\";s:5:\"group\";s:5:\"basic\";s:6:\"weight\";i:2;s:4:\"form\";a:3:{s:5:\"#type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"#rows\";i:2;s:8:\"#wysiwyg\";b:0;}s:4:\"name\";s:11:\"description\";}s:8:\"abstract\";a:7:{s:5:\"label\";s:8:\"Abstract\";s:11:\"description\";s:161:\"A brief and concise summary of the page\'s content, preferably 150 characters or less. The abstract meta tag may be used by search engines for archiving purposes.\";s:5:\"class\";s:17:\"DrupalTextMetaTag\";s:5:\"group\";s:5:\"basic\";s:6:\"weight\";i:3;s:4:\"form\";a:3:{s:5:\"#type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"#rows\";i:2;s:8:\"#wysiwyg\";b:0;}s:4:\"name\";s:8:\"abstract\";}s:8:\"keywords\";a:6:{s:5:\"label\";s:8:\"Keywords\";s:11:\"description\";s:122:\"A comma-separated list of keywords about the page. This meta tag is <e